=> Adding an IP Address to an Inerface
      Router(config)# interface g0/1 
      Router(config-if)# ip address 192.168.1.100 255.255.255.0

=> Removing the IP configuration from an Interface:
      Router(config)# interface Fa0/1
      Router(config-if)# no ip address

=> How to check the Bandwidth & Delay of an Interface:
      Router# show interface g0/1
